# Neutron Star Curvature Model
# COMAF × PNMS Addendum: CURVATURE + ENTROPY blocks
# Physical scenario: neutron star near nuclear saturation density.
# Ricci scalar at NS surface ≈ 4.2×10^42 Ricci-Bits (degenerate fermion gas regime).
# Paper reference: §3 COMAF × PNMS Addendum, §4 QULT-C Math
# Status: syntax demo + addendum coverage
ENTITY: NeutronStar
CYCLE: CPL-3
FRAME: t ∈ [0, 1 WarpTick]
UNITS: Planck

ENTROPY S:
  evolve Boltzmann {
    init: 1e57
    max: 1e58
    scale: 1e10 Plaseconds
  }

STABILITY:
  metric D = exp(-|∇S| · t)

CURVATURE R_ns: 4.2e42 RicciBits

ON cycle.end:
  S = S / (1 + alpha)
